 void	RB_ARB2_DrawInteraction( const drawInteraction_t *din ) {
+	// Iter 4/6: capture every lit-pass interaction this frame into the
+	// shared accumulator. The WebGPU backend replays them all into
+	// #webgpuCanvas at EndFrame using interaction.wgsl (one uniform slot
+	// per record). Skip tiny views (lightgem renders the player into a
+	// 64px viewport every frame — those records would draw a stray player
